import * as React from "react";
import Typography from "@mui/material/Typography";
import Container from "@mui/material/Container";
import placeholder from "../assets/img/placeholder-image.png";
import LLmock1 from "../assets/img/LL/LLmock1.png";
import LLmock2 from "../assets/img/LL/LLmock2.png";
import LLmock3 from "../assets/img/LL/LLmock3.png";
import LLmock32 from "../assets/img/LL/LLmock3-2.png";
import LLmock33 from "../assets/img/LL/LLmock3-3.png";
import LLtoday from "../assets/img/LL/LLtoday.png";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
import Box from "@mui/material/Box";
import { Ditto } from "ditto-react";
import { Paper } from "@mui/material";
import Button from "@mui/material/Button";
import Item from "@mui/material/Grid";

export default function Project1() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ mt: 8, flexGrow: 1 }}>
      {/** Project 1 - Pendo Customization */}

      <Grid containe spacing={2} m={16} bgcolor="blue">
        {/** Project Title */}
        <Grid xs={12}>
          <Typography variant="h4" align='center' gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf108" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>

        {/** Problem Statement */}
        <Grid>
          <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf10a" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf10c" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>

        {/** Key Result */}
        <Grid>
          <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf10e" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf110" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>

        {/** Journey */}
        <Grid xs={12}>
          <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf112" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid xs={8}>
          <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf114" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        {/** Early LL mockups */}

        <Grid xs={4}>
          <Container
            xs={6}
            md={4}
            component="img"
            src={LLmock1}
            maxWidth="sm"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Typography xs={6} md={8} variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf118" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        {/** Support Features */}
        <Container component="img" src={LLmock2} maxWidth="sm" />
        <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
          <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf11c" />
        </Typography>
        {/** Testing Results */}
        <Container component="img" src={placeholder} maxWidth="sm" />
        <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
          <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf120" />
        </Typography>
        {/** Final Design in XD */}
        <Container component="img" src={LLmock3} maxWidth="sm" />
        <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
          <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf124" />
        </Typography>

        {/** Final Implementation of LL */}
        <Grid>
          <Container component="img" src={LLtoday} maxWidth="sm" />
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf128" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
            <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf12a" />
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            href="https://go.pendo.io/Pendorama-December-2020.html"
          >
            View Presentation
          </Button>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      {/** Challenges */}
      <Grid>
        <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom component="div">
          <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf12c" />
        </Typography>
      </Grid>
      <Grid>
        <Typography variant="body" gutterBottom component="div">
          <Ditto textId="text_62f05a6f481a4aaf356bf12e" />
        </Typography>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}
